<div class='talk-article__body talk-transcript__body'>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1182' id='t-1182'>I have a vision for each one of you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='4641' id='t-4641'>and the vision I have for you</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='6469' id='t-6469'>is that when you wake up in the morning,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='8875' id='t-8875'>your blood is singing at the thought
of being who you are</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='12403' id='t-12403'>and doing what you do;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='14348' id='t-14348'>that as you go through the day,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='15904' id='t-15904'>you can literally sink
to your knees in gratitude</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='19411' id='t-19411'>at the tremendous good fortune
that's been bestowed on you;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='23566' id='t-23566'>that as you go through the day,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='25131' id='t-25131'>you become radiantly alive several times.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='31530' id='t-31530'>And if your life isn't like that,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='35417' id='t-35417'>I'd like to humbly suggest
that you're wasting your life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='38968' id='t-38968'>A life is too short to be wasted.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='41938' id='t-41938'>So what I propose to do
in the next 17 minutes --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='45098' id='t-45098'>I've used up one minute already --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='47113' id='t-47113'>is to give you a set of powerful tools</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='50597' id='t-50597'>which can get you started on being there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='54525' id='t-54525'>Is that of interest to you?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='55843' id='t-55843'>Audience: Yes.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:08
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='57018' id='t-57018'>Srikumar Rao: OK.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='58197' id='t-58197'>This is a conference on happiness,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='60116' id='t-60116'>but even if it wasn't
a conference on happiness,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='62675' id='t-62675'>would it be right if I said
