<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='67800' id='t-67800'>you're devoting your entire life</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='70029' id='t-70029'>to being happy?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='71586' id='t-71586'>Everything you do -- your job, family,
children, relationships, whatever --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='76414' id='t-76414'>is a quest for happiness.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='78600' id='t-78600'>Correct?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='79955' id='t-79955'>I'd like you to think about the following:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='83331' id='t-83331'>What do you have to get</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='86933' id='t-86933'>in order to be happy?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='89458' id='t-89458'>We're just going to spend
a minute on this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='91577' id='t-91577'>What do you have to get
in order to be happy?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='96411' id='t-96411'>Anybody, quick?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='98394' id='t-98394'>When I conduct this experiment,
a bunch of stuff comes up:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='101433' id='t-101433'>vast wealth, trophy spouse, good health,
