<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='113608' id='t-113608'>in order to be happy.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='116530' id='t-116530'>I would like you to consider this:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='118427' id='t-118427'>anything that you can get --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='121350' id='t-121350'>let me repeat that -- anything
