<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='378150' id='t-378150'>You've got your own variation on that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='380501' id='t-380501'>But it's the model itself that's flawed,
not what you put on the &quot;if&quot; side</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='385182' id='t-385182'>of the equation.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='386943' id='t-386943'>I can demonstrate that to you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='388942' id='t-388942'>Can any of you recall a time</span>
